snippet.title: Sonic Jump Fever Trailer
snippet.description:
In Sonic Jump Fever, compete against your friends for high scores in fast vertical jumping challenges. Unleash Fever Mode and push Sonic into hyper-speed for earth-shattering scores.

Coming to the App Store and Google Play Store for free this summer!
